OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1780330269
OL,3,C'Nearly all' of Plymouth Argyle Women
OL,4,Csquad let go via email
OL,6,FPlymouth Argyle Women players have
OL,7,Fresponded after they were allegedly
OL,8,Ftold via email that the majority of
OL,9,Fthe team will be released from their
OL,10,Fcontracts next month.
OL,12,FIt comes just weeks after the team
OL,13,Fnarrowly missed out on promotion to
OL,14,Fthe Women's Super League 2 at the end
OL,15,Fof what players called the team's
OL,16,F"most successful season in history".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
