PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1780330269
OL,3,C'Nearly all' of Plymouth Argyle Women
OL,4,Csquad let go via email
OL,6,F"Throughout the season, we were told
OL,7,Fthat the club had ambition, that it
OL,8,Fwas building towards becoming a full-
OL,9,Ftime professional outfit, and that
OL,10,Fwomen's football was important to the
OL,11,Ffootball club," players said in a
OL,12,Fstatement.
OL,14,F"That is why the events of recent
OL,15,Fweeks have been so difficult to
OL,16,Funderstand.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
