OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1780330269
OL,3,C'Nearly all' of Plymouth Argyle Women
OL,4,Csquad let go via email
OL,6,F"Following a decision from the board
OL,7,Fto significantly reduce the team's
OL,8,Fbudget, and the understandable
OL,9,Fresignation of our manager, nearly all
OL,10,Fplayers have been informed via an
OL,11,Femail from the club that they will be
OL,12,Freleased at the end of our contracts
OL,13,Fnext month."
OL,15,FThey added they were disappointed by
OL,16,Fhow the matter was handled, describing
OL,17,Fthe email as cold and impersonal.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
