OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1780330269
OL,3,C'Nearly all' of Plymouth Argyle Women
OL,4,Csquad let go via email
OL,6,FOn 28 May 2026 former FA Cup-winning
OL,7,Fgoalkeeper Marie Hourihan resigned
OL,8,Fafter 12 months as Head Coach at the
OL,9,Fclub.
OL,11,FIn the statement announcing her
OL,12,Fdeparture, she alluded to changes in
OL,13,Fdirection and how "people can become
OL,14,Funaligned".
OL,16,F"For that reason now is the right time
OL,17,Ffor me to consolidate and consider
OL,18,Fwhat is next for me," she said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1780330269
OL,3,C'Nearly all' of Plymouth Argyle Women
OL,4,Csquad let go via email
OL,6,F"This has not been a decision I have
OL,7,Ftaken lightly, particularly because of
OL,8,Fthe potential and the people here
OL,9,Finvested in the women's project."
OL,11,FPlymouth Argyle have been approached
OL,12,Ffor comment.
OL,14,FIn April 2026 the club revealed it
OL,15,Ffaced debts of more than #10.5 million
OL,16,Fand made 18 people redundant within
OL,17,Fone week.
OL,19,FOwner Simon Hallett added that rising
OL,20,Fcosts, particularly electricity, were
OL,21,Fbecoming "hard to respond to".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1780330269
OL,3,C'Nearly all' of Plymouth Argyle Women
OL,4,Csquad let go via email
OL,6,F"While we are hurt, this is about more
OL,7,Fthan just our squad. It is about the
OL,8,Fnegative message being sent to women
OL,9,Fand girls across Plymouth, our wider
OL,10,Ffanbase, the South West and the
OL,11,Fbroader football community," the Women
OL,12,Fplayers said in the statement.
OL,14,F"We hope that one day women and girls
OL,15,Fcan once again look to Plymouth Argyle
OL,16,Fas a club that advocates for the
OL,17,Fwomen's game, drives progress and
OL,18,Fcreates a clear pathway for football
OL,19,Fto grow in our region."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
